

**Mamtsh am i bei g Jesus geꞌe kownal wui **

*An g neid g Matthew 27:1-2, 11-14; Luke 23:1-5; John 18:28-38 *

1 Tsh am wabsh i chum mahsi. Tsh am ep e nam hegam uꞌugchu papal ch geꞌeged ch chehanig t‑mashchamdam mo d e jehnigiddam k atsh am i mamche mat has hahawa ep wo e juh. Tsh am i kuhgit g ha‑namki. Kutsh am si maniadad g Jesus nohnhoi k gam hu be k am uꞌapa heg wui mo d kownal ch hab chehgig Pilate ab abchudch mo chum e kownalchud. 

2 Kush ihda Pilate ab kakke g Jesus, “No wa woho mapsh hab chum e elid map d ha‑kownalig idam Tutuligo hemajkam?” 

Sh hab kaij g Jesus, “Dani ahni.” 

3 Sh g uꞌugchu papal muꞌi haꞌichu ab abchud. Sh pi am hu has shaꞌi kaij g Jesus. 

4 Sh g Pilate ab ep kakke, “Neh, muꞌi haꞌichu o ab m‑abchud. Napt pi am hu has wo shaꞌi chei ab amjed?” 

5 Kush ep pi am hu has shaꞌi ha kaij g Jesus. Tsh g Pilate si has i e taht heg hekaj. 

**Mamtsh ab mohtoꞌi g Jesus mat wo muh **

*An g neid g Matthew 27:15-26; Luke 23:13-25; John 18:39–19:16 *

6 K am hab e wua ahid ab id eda gegosig mo g kownal am hema i dadagitod g lihso am ha wehhejed g hemajkam. 7 Kush eda am haꞌi kuhpi g lilso matsh haꞌi ha kokda am i chum wushshadch g kownal. Sh hema hab chehgig idam Barabbas. 

8 Kutsh g hemajkam ab i kakke g Pilate matsh am hab hig wo ha juni hegai mash chum hekid am hab ha wuijid. 

9 Sh g Pilate ab ha kakke, “Pegih, nam hab elid mant id am wo i dagito am em‑wehhejed mash d em‑kownalig?” nash pi chum s‑dagitoimk g Jesus 10 ch hab ha elid mo d waꞌi idam uꞌugchu papal ch s‑hehgamk ch s‑muꞌamk. 

11 Kutsh wabshaba g uꞌugchu papal am i ha cheha g hemajkam matsh hab wo chei matsh g Barabbas wo e dagito. Kutsh wa woho am hab e juh. 

12 Kush hab ep kaij g Pilate, “Pegih, kunt has wo juh ihda oꞌodham mam hab aꞌaga mo d em‑kownalig?” 

13 Kush si s‑kaidam hab kaij g hemajkam, “Muꞌani ab kots t ab\!” 

14 Kutsh hab chum chei g Pilate, “Haschu ahg? Shahchu at hig pi ap has juh?” 

Kush oi wa wabsh baꞌich i si s‑kaidam hab wabsh ge kaij muꞌikko, “Muꞌani\! Muꞌani ab kots t ab.” 

15 Kush g Pilate tatchua mat wo s‑hohhoꞌi g hemajkam ch atsh heg hekaj am i dagito g Barabbas am ha wui k am ha cheha g shondal mat am wo gewitta g Jesus. Kumtsh wa woho hab juh. Tsh am hahawa ha wui dagito matsh gam hu wo be k ab wo naggia kots t ab. 

**Mash g shondal wabsh nahnko wua g Jesus **

*An g neid g Matthew 27:27-31; John 19:2-3 *

16 Kutsh gam hu hahawa i bei g shondal g Jesus kownal geꞌe kih am k am wehs ha wai g e‑wehm shondal. 17 Kutsh am i e hemapad k nahnko wua. Msh wa ab abchud mash chum e kownalchud. Pegih, tsh ab wahki g kownal eniga k ge hoꞌi gihkot k ab wahki moꞌoj ab. 18 Kush hab wabsh s‑ahgamk ch hab kaij, “Tash g d ha‑kownaligk g Tutuligo hemajkam.” 19 Tsh haꞌi an si gewitta moꞌoj an g uhskaj k ab siswuimad k ab wui i shul pehegia ab has elidch. 20 Kumtsh am i haꞌasa nahnkogid k am si wuahawua hegai kownal eniga k ab uhpam wahki g enigaj k gam hu hahawa i bei mat ab wo naggia kots t ab. 

**Mamtsh ab naggia g Jesus kots t ab **

*An g neid g Matthew 27:32-44; Luke 23:26-43; John 19:17-27 *

21 D ab hema i ha nam g oꞌodham ch ab him Jerusalem wui ch ash hab chehgig Simon. Id ad an bei g shondal k ab kushwiotach hegai kots mamt ab ab wo naggia g Jesus. Ihda Simon ash ab d kihkam Cyrene kihhim t ab ch d ha‑ohg idam Alexander ch Rufus. 

22 Kumd gam hu i bei g Jesus mam am ha nahngia. K hab e aꞌaga amai Golgotha mo id hab d ahga Koshwak. 23 Kumd am chum iꞌich g nawait ch kulani mat wo hehogih g s‑koꞌok. Kud pi shaꞌi ih g Jesus. 

24 Kumd ab hahawa sisish kots t ab k am kei g kots. D am haꞌi e chichwi g shondal k wo nei mas hedai haschu wo bei g haꞌichu enigaj. 25 K eda ga hu i juhk madki heki hu e ai g humukt ohla mamd ab naggia kots t ab. 

26 D an oꞌohanas g ha‑abchuda ab dahm mo ab i moꞌokch g Jesus ch hab chuꞌig, “Id o d ha‑Kownalig g Tutuligo Hemajkam.” 

27 Kumd gohk ab ep ha nahngia kokots t ab gan hu aꞌai. Sh eda d s‑chu eꞌeskam idam. \[ 28 Kum hab masma am chehgidch mam hab elid mo g Jesus hab waꞌap d pi ap hemajkam. Neh, heki o hu an oꞌohanas Jiosh oꞌohana ed mat id am hab wo e juh.\] 

29 D hegam mo am bihbimhim nahnko ahg ch hab ahg, “Naptsh woho wo i wua g geꞌe cheopi k am uhpam ep wo i kei waik tash ab? 30 Pegih, ab g hig i huduni kots t amjed k wo e doꞌibia maptp wo e nako.” 

31 D g uꞌugchu papal ch chehanig t‑mashchamdam am hab waꞌap nahnko ahg hab kaijch ab aꞌai e wui, “Id atsh haꞌi ha doꞌibia k atki wabshaba pi wo e nako mas wo hejel e doꞌibia. 32 Nash hig pi woho d Jiosh si Kehsha ch d t‑kownalig? Pegih, tt ab wo s‑wohoch matp ab wo i huduni k wo e doꞌibia.” D hegam ehp mad ab wehmaj nahngia hab waꞌap nahnko ahg. 

**Matsh muh g Jesus **

*An g neid g Matthew 27:45-56; Luke 23:44-49; John 19:28-30 *

33 D am i dahm juh. D wehsko gei g s‑chuhugam waik ohla ab. 34 D am i e ai g waik ohla. D si s‑kaidam hab kaij g Jesus, “Eloi, Eloi, lama sabaktani.” Id o hab d ahga, “Ni‑Jioshga, ni‑Jioshga, pt haschu ahgk wabsh ni‑dagito?” 

35 D haꞌijj hab kaij hegam mad am gegok, “Nehꞌe, Elijabad o ab chum waid.” 

36 Kud am hema med k an haꞌichu usko mad am wakch nawait ch ed k am uhgk i be k ab chum iꞌich g Jesus k hab chei, “Kia koi, tt hig wo nei mas ia wo jiwia g Elijabad k ab wo i huduni.” 

37 Kud am si s‑kaidam haꞌichu hab ep chei g Jesus k am hahawa i muh. 

38 Kutsh hegai s‑kowk ikus kuhpadag mash am s‑tadnim naggia ged hu si eda g geꞌe cheopi ab si shel e wantsh. 

39 D hegai moki d shondal ha‑geꞌejig gahab kehk kots wui ch am kah g Jesus ch am neid mat has masma muh ch hab kaij, “Ihda oki si s‑wohom d alidaj g Jiosh.” 

40 D ga hu sha mehkjed g uꞌuwi ab haꞌi neid mat haschu has e juh. Haꞌi idam o d Salome ch Mary Magdalene ch hegai Mary mo d ha‑jeꞌe idam James ch Joses. 41 Idam waik ash am wehmaj oiopohim g Jesus ch haꞌichukaj i wehmt mo eda gam hu oimmelhim Galilee chekshani ch ed. Kud muꞌi idam uꞌuwi am wehmaj ab i hihi g Jesus Jerusalem wui. 

**Matsh ged hu e cheh g Jesus **

*An g neid g Matthew 27:57-61; Luke 23:50-56; John 19:38-42 *

42-43 D am haꞌichug hegai e jehnigiddam mo ab Arimathea t amjed ch hab chehgig Joseph. Id o si s‑ap d oꞌodham ch ab s‑neidamk g Jiosh kownaltalig. D eda e aihim mat wo i hud. Kuchd eda am chum t‑nakog matt baꞌich i tash wo chum t‑mihshmad. D heg hekaj am hih ihda Joseph k atsh ab tai g kownal g Jesus honshpadag. 

44 Kush g Pilate hab kaij, “A nat wa s‑wohom heki hu i muh?” atsh am hahawa wai g shondal ha‑geꞌejig. 45 Sh id hab kaij mat heki hu muh. 

Kush hab hahawa ahg g Joseph mo am wa s‑ape mat am wo bei. 

46 Kutsh g Joseph am him k am ha nolawt g si s‑kehg ikus k am ep jiwia. Kumd am wehhejed ab i huduni g Jesus honshpadag. K am mia hab chuꞌig g hihaꞌini ch ab heki hu cheotas hodai ch ed. Kumd am i be k ged hu heg eda cheh am i hobinodk heg hekaj s‑kehg ikus. Kumd ab hahawa kuh g geꞌe hodaikaj. 47 D g Mary Magdalene ch hegai Mary mo d ha‑jeꞌe g James ch Joses am wa neid mad hebai e cheh. 

